/
.Fl -no-u .
.It Fl -uid
Add the numeric user ID column to the long listing.
Suppressor:
.Fl -no-uid .
.It Fl g , Fl -group
Add the group column to the long listing.
The group is coloured in three tiers: your primary group, a
