Suppressor:
.Fl -no-group
/
.Fl -no-g .
.It Fl -gid
Add the numeric group ID column to the long listing.
Suppressor:
.Fl -no-gid .
.It Fl m , Fl -modified
Add the modified timestamp column to the long listing.
Suppressor:
.Fl -no-modified
/
